  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><br>Take your mouse and try to reach the exit of the maze <strong>without touching walls</strong> and <strong>before the end of the timer</strong>.<br><br>Will you try to beat your best score if you lose?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Very simple gameplay, you only need a mouse to play<br></li><li> Unlimited playing time with the procedural maze generation<br></li><li> Progressive difficulty<br></li><li> Your score is saved for the next time<br></li><li> Three different endings</li></ul>",
